com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist
Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.Preferences

public final class Preferences
extends Object

This class contains all preferences that the user might change at runtime. It serves as a facade abstracting Moneydance's UserPreferences (received from the FeatureModuleContext) and the hard-wired default values used in stand-alone mode from the rest of the extension.

Author:
Florian J. Breunig
